ayer)\n** [[Viasat]] (TV3+, TV3 Sport 1, TV3 Sport 2, Viaplay)\n*'''[[Davis Cup]]'''\n** [[Canal 8 Sport]], [[Canal 9 (Denmark)|Canal 9]]\n*'''[[The Championships, Wimbledon|Wimbledon]]'''\n** [[Viasat]] (TV3+, TV3 Sport 1, TV3 Sport 2)\n*'''[[Australian Open]]'''\n** [[Discovery Communications|Discovery]] (Eurosport Danmark, Eurosport Player)\n*'''[[US Open (tennis)|US Open]]'''\n** [[Discovery Communications|Discovery]] (Eurosport Danmark, Eurosport Player)\n*'''[[French Open]]'''\n** [[Discovery Communications|Discovery]] (Eurosport Danmark, Eurosport Player)\n\n== Baseball ==\n\n*'''[[Major League Baseball]]'''\n** [[Discovery Communications|Discovery]] (6'eren, Eurosport Danmark, Eurosport Player)\n\n== Basketball ==\n\n*'''[[National Basketball Association]]'''\n** [[TV2 Denmark]] (TV2 Sport)\n*'''Basketball ligaen (Danish league)'''\n** [[TV2 Denmark]] (TV2 Sport)\n\n== Badminton ==\n\n*'''Danish Badminton League'''\n** [[Viasat]] (TV3 Sport 1, TV3 Sport 2, Viaplay)\n*'''Yonex DM (Danish tournament)'''\n** [[Viasat]] (TV3 Sport 1, TV3 Sport 2, Viaplay)\n*[[Badminton World Federation|'''BWF''']]\n**[[TV2 Denmark]] (TV2 Sport)\n*'''[[Copenhagen Masters|Yonex Copenhagen Masters]] (Danish tournament)'''\n** [[Viasat]] (TV3 Sport 1, TV3 Sport 2, Viaplay)\n\n== Motorsports ==\n\n*'''[[Speedway Grand Prix]]'''\n** [[Viasat]] (TV3+, TV3 Sport 1, TV3 Sport 2, Viaplay)\n*'''[[Speedway World Cup]]'''\n** [[Viasat]] (TV3+, TV3 Sport 1, TV3 Sport 2, Viaplay)\n*'''[[Elitserien (speedway)|Elitserien]]'''\n** [[Discovery Communications|Discovery]] (Eurosport Danmark, Eurosport Player)\n*'''[[IndyCar Series]]'''\n** [[Discovery Communications|Discovery]] (Eurosport Danmark, Eurosport Player)\n*'''[[NASCAR]]'''\n** [[Discovery Communications|Discovery]] (Eurosport Danmark, Eurosport Player)\n*'''[[Formel 1]]'''\n** [[Viasat]] (TV3+, TV3 Sport 1, TV3 Sport 2, Viasat XTRA, Viaplay)\n*'''[[Scandinavian Touring Car Championship]]'''\n** C-More ([[Canal 8 Sport]], [[Canal 9 (Denmark)|Canal 9]], C More Play)\n*'''[[24 Hours of Le Mans]]'''\n** [[TV2 Denmark]]\n** [[Discovery Communications|Discovery]] (Eurosport, Eurosport Player)\n*'''[[World Rally Championship]]'''\n** [[Viasat]] (TV3+, TV3 Sport 1, TV3 Sport 2, Viaplay)\n*'''[[Moto GP]]'''\n** [[Viasat]] (TV3 Sport 2, Viasat XTRA, Viaplay)\n*'''Deutsche Tourenwagen Masters (DTM)'''\n** [[Viasat]] (TV3+, TV3 Sport 1, TV3 Sport 2, Viaplay)\n\n== Fighting ==\n\n*'''[[Ultimate Fighting Championship|UFC]]'''\n** [[Discovery Communications|Discovery]] (Eurosport Danmark, Eurosport Player)\n*'''[[ONE Championship]]'''\n**[[FITE TV]]\n*'''[[Bellator MMA]]'''\n**[[Discovery Communications|Discovery]] (Eurosport Danmark, Eurosport Player)\n*'''[[World Extreme Cagefighting]]'''\n** [[Discovery Communications|Discovery]] (Eurosport Danmark, Eurosport Player)\n\n* '''[[Cage Warriors]]'''\n** [[Viasat]] (TV3+, TV3 Sport 1, TV3 Sport 2, Viaplay)\n\n*'''Rumble Of The Kings'''\n**[[Discovery Communications|Discovery]] (Eurosport Danmark, Eurosport Player)\n*'''Nordic Fight Night'''\n**[[Viasat]] (TV3+, TV3 Sport 1, TV3 Sport 2, Viaplay)\n*'''Some Boxing Events'''\n**[[Viasat]] (TV3+, TV3 Sport 1, TV3 Sport 2, Viaplay)\n**[[Discovery Communications|Discovery]] (Eurosport Danmark, Eurosport Player)\n*'''[[WWE]]'''\n**[[Discovery Communications|Discovery]] (Eurosport Danmark, Eurosport Player)\n\n== Golf ==\n\n*'''[[Ryder Cup]]'''\n** [[Viasat Golf]], Viaplay\n*'''[[PGA Tour]]'''\n** [[Viasat Golf]], Viaplay\n*'''[[European Tour]]'''\n** [[Viasat Golf]], Viaplay\n*'''[[British Open]]'''\n** [[Viasat Golf]], Viaplay\n*'''[[PGA Championship]]'''\n** [[Viasat Golf]], Viaplay\n*'''[[World Golf Championships]]'''\n** [[Viasat Golf]], Viaplay\n*'''[[US Masters]]'''\n** [[Viasat]] (TV3 Sport 1, TV3 Sport 2, Viaplay)\n\n== Athletics ==\n\n*'''[[Samsung Diamond League]]'''\n** [[Viasat]] (TV3 Sport 1, TV3 Sport 2, Viaplay)\n\n== Volleyball ==\n\n*'''European Championship (men)'''\n** [[Viasat]] (TV3 Sport 1, TV3 Sport 